==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Driftwood
<hw>Drift"wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Wood
drifted or floated by water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: Whatever is drifting or floating as on
water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The current of humanity, with its heavy proportion of very useless
<qex>driftwood</qex>.</q> <rj><qau> New Your Times.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drifty</ent>⟦br⟧
